OL,3,CMPs debate emergency law to save
OL,4,CBritish Steel in rare Saturday sitting
OL,6,FMPs are sitting in an emergency
OL,7,Fparliament session today to debate a
OL,8,Flaw aimed at saving British Steel's
OL,9,FScunthorpe plant from imminent closure.
OL,11,FThe Steel Industry (Special Measures)
OL,12,FBill would give the business secretary
OL,13,Fthe powers to prevent the Chinese
OL,14,Fowner of the plant, Jingye, from
OL,15,Fclosing blast furnaces at the site.
