OL,3,CMPs debate emergency law to save
OL,4,CBritish Steel in rare Saturday sitting
OL,6,FThe Bill, which the government
OL,7,Fpublished ahead of the debate on
OL,8,FSaturday, allows the government to
OL,9,Finstruct steel companies to keep
OL,10,Fassets running, and to take over those
OL,11,Fassets if they fail to comply with
OL,12,Fthose instructions.
OL,14,FIt also provides for a compensation
OL,15,Fscheme for costs incurred by the
OL,16,Fcompany following the government's
OL,17,Finstructions, and criminal sanctions
OL,18,Ffor executives who disregard them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
