OL,3,CMPs debate emergency law to save
OL,4,CBritish Steel in rare Saturday sitting
OL,6,FThe Bill is being introduced by
OL,7,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds,
OL,8,Fwho will then open the debate. Shadow
OL,9,FBusiness Secretary Andrew Griffith
OL,10,Fwill then respond.
OL,12,FMr Reynolds said the legislation is
OL,13,F"unequivocally in our national
OL,14,Finterests". The Leader of the Commons,
OL,15,FLucy Powell, urged MPs to act
OL,16,F"decisively" and "at a pace" to ensure
OL,17,Ffurnaces are kept going to save the
OL,18,Fdomestic production of virgin steel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
