OL,6,FBut Alex Burghart, who was acting as
OL,7,Fshadow Commons leader, told MPs the
OL,8,Fgovernment had "made a total pig's
OL,9,Fbreakfast of the whole arrangement."
OL,11,F"The fact of the matter is anyone who
OL,12,Fhas been paying any attention to this
OL,13,Fstory over the past few months has
OL,14,Fknown this was coming down the track,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
