OL,6,FJingye said the business is running at
OL,7,Fa loss of #700,000 a day maintaining
OL,8,Fthe plant. They claim the plant's two
OL,9,Fblast furnaces are no longer
OL,10,Ffinancially sustainable and the raw
OL,11,Fmaterials needed to keep them
OL,12,Foperational are running out.
