OL,3,CMPs debate emergency law to save
OL,4,CBritish Steel in rare Saturday sitting
OL,6,FThe business secretary described the
OL,7,Flegislation as a "proportionate and
OL,8,Fnecessary step," telling MPs it would
OL,9,F"allow us to take control of British
OL,10,FSteel's blast furnaces, maintaining
OL,11,Fsteel production and by extension
OL,12,Fprotecting the company's 3,500-strong
OL,13,Fworkforce."
OL,15,FThe business secretary stressed that
OL,16,Fthe measures, while they would allow
OL,17,Fthe government to "take control of the
OL,18,Fsituation", would be "temporary."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
