OL,6,FShadow Business Secretary Andrew
OL,7,FGriffith argued that today is "not a
OL,8,Ffailure by the steelworkers of
OL,9,FScunthorpe", but instead a "failure on
OL,10,Fthe government's watch".
OL,12,F"This is a botched nationalisation
OL,13,Fplan revealing the government has no
OL,14,Fplan," he said.
OL,16,FHe accused the government of being
OL,17,Fslow to legislate, saying they had
OL,18,Fshown "indefensible incompetence."
